OL,3,CFather who died after being hit by car
OL,4,Chad 'unsurvivable' injuries
OL,6,FA father who died after being hit by a
OL,7,Fcar would not have survived his
OL,8,Finjuries, an inquest into his death
OL,9,Fhas heard.
OL,11,F27-year-old Thomas Hunter, from
OL,12,FSwadlincote, was walking on Burton
OL,13,FRoad near Ashby-de-la-Zouch in
OL,14,FDecember 2023 when he was hit by a
OL,15,Fsports car, travelling in the opposite
OL,16,Fdirection.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784825276
OL,3,CFather who died after being hit by car
OL,4,Chad 'unsurvivable' injuries
OL,6,FThe car - an American Pontiac Firebird
OL,7,F- struck Mr Hunter head-on, knocking
OL,8,Fhim into a hedgerow. The father of
OL,9,Fone's body was found by police 24
OL,10,Fhours later.
OL,12,FA postmortem examination into his
OL,13,Fdeath concluded he died by a head
OL,14,Finjury and he would have been killed
OL,15,Falmost immediately on impact.
OL,17,FThe inquest also heard Mr Hunter's
OL,18,Fbody was so deeply embedded in the
OL,19,Fhedge that it had to be retrieved by
OL,20,Fthree people.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784825276
OL,3,CFather who died after being hit by car
OL,4,Chad 'unsurvivable' injuries
OL,6,FBrandon Beesla, 27, admitted driving a
OL,7,Fvehicle likely to cause danger of
OL,8,Finjury. He was given a 12-month
OL,9,Fdriving ban and fined.
OL,11,FEvidence given at the inquest found
OL,12,Fthere was no street lighting on Burton
OL,13,FRoad and that weather conditions were
OL,14,Frainy.
OL,16,FThe car had passed its MOT 16 days
OL,17,Fearlier and given the road conditions
OL,18,Fand the speed the car was travelling,
OL,19,Fthe driver would not have been able to
OL,20,Fstop in time, the inquest heard.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784825276
OL,3,CFather who died after being hit by car
OL,4,Chad 'unsurvivable' injuries
OL,6,FIt also heard there was no evidence Mr
OL,7,FHunter's body had been moved or
OL,8,Fdragged into the hedgerow.
OL,10,FSeveral members of Thomas Hunter's
OL,11,Ffamily were at the inquest, including
OL,12,Fhis partner Chloe Mefford, who has
OL,13,Fchallenged Leicestershire Police's
OL,14,Finvestigation previously saying they
OL,15,Fdid not ask enough questions at the
OL,16,Ftime of the incident.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784825276
OL,3,CFather who died after being hit by car
OL,4,Chad 'unsurvivable' injuries
OL,6,FMs Mefford has filed several
OL,7,Fcomplaints in relation to the
OL,8,Fincident, including one which is now
OL,9,Fbeing reviewed by the Independent
OL,10,FOffice for Police Conduct.
OL,12,FThe Coroner, however, stated the
OL,13,Finquest would not involve any elements
OL,14,Fof a criminal investigation, and that
OL,15,FMr Hunter died as a result of a road
OL,16,Ftraffic collision.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/5
